Tress MacNeille https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tress_MacNeille 0 Tress MacNeille (born Teressa Claire Payne; June 20, 1951) is an American voice actress, who has voiced various characters in shows like The Simpsons, Futurama, Hey Arnold!, Tiny Toon Adventures, Rugrats, Animaniacs and Disney's House of Mouse.
